definition: on full rudder/turning as sharply as possible

sentences.english: We deviated in our navigation. Please turn right full rudder.
sentences.chinese: 航行的方向出現偏差，請右滿舵行駛。

sentences.english: I am steering hard-a-starboard at speed available so as to stay clear of the fairway.
sentences.chinese: 我船正在打右滿舵以剩餘的船速行駛，以便離開航道。

sentences.english: Full right rudder, we are not staying here.
